name: Analog Journey - Rage Against Humanity
description: Unleashed from the dooms of hell, this beast has to be slain in order to save the world we know and love. Will you be the hero to conquer que monster, and bring back glory to your people? "Analog Journey is a small collection of simulated chiptunes, made with 'Analog' instrument on Ableton. It is the synthesis of my path, my story and my feelings, presented to you in 8 bits."
